<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">

    <title>Panel de Administración - Cafetería</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/source/css/diseño.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container-fluid py-4">
        <!-- Lista de empleados -->
        <div class="card shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-header bg-white">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <h5 class="mb-0" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">
                        <i class="fas fa-list me-2"></i>Lista de Empleados
                    </h5>
                    <div>
                        <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary me-2" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#addEmployeeModal" style="font-size: 0.7rem;">
                            <i class="fas fa-plus me-1"></i> Agregar
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <!-- Búsqueda y filtros -->
                <div class="row mb-2">
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-2">
                        <div class="search-bar">
                            <i class="fas fa-search search-icon"></i>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm" id="searchEmployees" placeholder="Buscar empleados...">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 d-flex justify-content-md-end">
                        <div class="dropdown">
                            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary dropdown-toggle" type="button" id="statusFilterDropdown" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false" style="font-size: 0.7rem;">
                                <i class="fas fa-filter me-1"></i> Estado
                            </button>
                            <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="statusFilterDropdown">
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#" style="font-size: 0.75rem;">Todos</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#" style="font-size: 0.75rem;">Activos</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#" style="font-size: 0.75rem;">Inactivos</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Tabla de empleados -->
                <div class="table-responsive">
                    <table class="table table-hover align-middle">
                        <thead>
                            <tr style="background-color: #FAF5F0;">
                                <th scope="col" width="40">#</th>
                                <th scope="col">Empleado</th>
                                <th scope="col">Contacto</th>
                                <th scope="col">Puesto</th>
                                <th scope="col" width="80">Estado</th>
                                <th scope="col" width="150">Acciones</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <th scope="row">1</th>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <img src="/api/placeholder/40/40" class="employee-avatar me-2" alt="Foto empleado">
                                        <div>
                                            <p class="employee-name mb-0">Carlos Rodríguez</p>
                                            <small class="employee-username">carlos_barista</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="contact-info">carlos.rodriguez@cafearoma.com</div>
                                    <small class="contact-phone">555-123-4567</small>
                                </td>
                                <td><span class="badge role-badge" style="background-color: #C8A780 !important;">Barista</span></td>
                                <td><span class="status-dot active"></span><small>Activo</small></td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="d-flex gap-1">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-info btn-action" title="Ver historial" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#historyModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-history"></i>
                                        </button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-warning btn-action" title="Editar" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#editEmployeeModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-edit"></i>
                                        </button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary btn-action" title="Deshabilitar" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#disableEmployeeModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-ban"></i>
                                        </button>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th scope="row">2</th>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <img src="/api/placeholder/40/40" class="employee-avatar me-2" alt="Foto empleado">
                                        <div>
                                            <p class="employee-name mb-0">Laura Martínez</p>
                                            <small class="employee-username">laura_chef</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="contact-info">laura.martinez@cafearoma.com</div>
                                    <small class="contact-phone">555-234-5678</small>
                                </td>
                                <td><span class="badge role-badge" style="background-color: #496F5D !important; color: white !important;">Chef</span></td>
                                <td><span class="status-dot inactive"></span><small>Inactivo</small></td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="d-flex gap-1">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-info btn-action" title="Ver historial" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#historyModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-history"></i>
                                        </button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-warning btn-action" title="Editar" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#editEmployeeModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-edit"></i>
                                        </button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-success btn-action" title="Habilitar" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#enableEmployeeModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                                        </button>

                                    </div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th scope="row">3</th>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <img src="/api/placeholder/40/40" class="employee-avatar me-2" alt="Foto empleado">
                                        <div>
                                            <p class="employee-name mb-0">Miguel Sánchez</p>
                                            <small class="employee-username">miguel_camarero</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="contact-info">miguel.sanchez@cafearoma.com</div>
                                    <small class="contact-phone">555-345-6789</small>
                                </td>
                                <td><span class="badge role-badge" style="background-color: #A67B5B !important; color: white !important;">Camarero</span></td>
                                <td><span class="status-dot active"></span><small>Activo</small></td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="d-flex gap-1">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-info btn-action" title="Ver historial" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#historyModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-history"></i>
                                        </button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-warning btn-action" title="Editar" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#editEmployeeModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-edit"></i>
                                        </button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary btn-action" title="Deshabilitar" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#disableEmployeeModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-ban"></i>
                                        </button>

                                    </div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th scope="row">4</th>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <img src="/api/placeholder/40/40" class="employee-avatar me-2" alt="Foto empleado">
                                        <div>
                                            <p class="employee-name mb-0">Ana López</p>
                                            <small class="employee-username">ana_cajera</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="contact-info">ana.lopez@cafearoma.com</div>
                                    <small class="contact-phone">555-456-7890</small>
                                </td>
                                <td><span class="badge bg-info text-dark role-badge" style="background-color: #6F4E37 !important; color: white !important;">Cajera</span></td>
                                <td><span class="status-dot active"></span><small>Activo</small></td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="d-flex gap-1">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-info btn-action" title="Ver historial" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#historyModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-history"></i>
                                        </button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-warning btn-action" title="Editar" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#editEmployeeModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-edit"></i>
                                        </button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary btn-action" title="Deshabilitar" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#disableEmployeeModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-ban"></i>
                                        </button>

                                    </div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th scope="row">5</th>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <img src="/api/placeholder/40/40" class="employee-avatar me-2" alt="Foto empleado">
                                        <div>
                                            <p class="employee-name mb-0">Javier Gómez</p>
                                            <small class="employee-username">javier_gerente</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="contact-info">javier.gomez@cafearoma.com</div>
                                    <small class="contact-phone">555-567-8901</small>
                                </td>
                                <td><span class="badge bg-info text-dark role-badge" style="background-color: #5D4037 !important; color: white !important;">Gerente</span></td>
                                <td><span class="status-dot active"></span><small>Activo</small></td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="d-flex gap-1">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-info btn-action" title="Ver historial" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#historyModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-history"></i>
                                        </button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-warning btn-action" title="Editar" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#editEmployeeModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-edit"></i>
                                        </button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary btn-action" title="Deshabilitar" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#disableEmployeeModal">
                                            <i class="fas fa-ban"></i>
                                        </button>

                                    </div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <!-- Paginación -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Modal Agregar Empleado -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="addEmployeeModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="addEmployeeModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="addEmployeeModalLabel">Agregar Nuevo Empleado</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <form>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="firstName" class="form-label">Nombre</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="firstName" placeholder="Ingrese nombre">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="lastName" class="form-label">Apellido</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="lastName" placeholder="Ingrese apellido">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="username" class="form-label">Nombre de usuario</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username" placeholder="Ingrese nombre de usuario">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="role" class="form-label">Puesto</label>
                                <select class="form-select" id="role">
                                    <option selected disabled>Seleccione un puesto</option>
                                    <option value="barista">Barista</option>
                                    <option value="chef">Chef</option>
                                    <option value="camarero">Camarero</option>
                                    <option value="cajero">Cajero</option>
                                    <option value="gerente">Gerente</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="email" class="form-label">Correo electrónico</label>
                                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Ingrese email">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="phone" class="form-label">Teléfono</label>
                                <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="phone" placeholder="Ingrese teléfono">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="password" class="form-label">Contraseña</label>
                                <div class="input-group">
                                    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" placeholder="Ingrese contraseña">
                                    <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" type="button" onclick="togglePassword('password')">
                                        <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="confirmPassword" class="form-label">Confirmar contraseña</label>
                                <div class="input-group">
                                    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="confirmPassword" placeholder="Confirme contraseña">
                                    <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" type="button" onclick="togglePassword('confirmPassword')">
                                        <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="profilePicture" class="form-label">Foto de perfil</label>
                            <input class="form-control" type="file" id="profilePicture">
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cancelar</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Guardar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Modal Editar Empleado -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="editEmployeeModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="editEmployeeModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="editEmployeeModalLabel">Editar Empleado</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <form>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="editFirstName" class="form-label">Nombre</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="editFirstName" value="Carlos">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="editLastName" class="form-label">Apellido</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="editLastName" value="Rodríguez">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="editUsername" class="form-label">Nombre de usuario</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="editUsername" value="carlos_barista">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="editRole" class="form-label">Puesto</label>
                                <select class="form-select" id="editRole">
                                    <option value="barista" selected>Barista</option>
                                    <option value="chef">Chef</option>
                                    <option value="camarero">Camarero</option>
                                    <option value="cajero">Cajero</option>
                                    <option value="gerente">Gerente</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="editEmail" class="form-label">Correo electrónico</label>
                                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="editEmail" value="carlos.rodriguez@cafearoma.com">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                <label for="editPhone" class="form-label">Teléfono</label>
                                <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="editPhone" value="555-123-4567">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="editProfilePicture" class="form-label">Actualizar foto de perfil</label>
                            <input class="form-control" type="file" id="editProfilePicture">
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <div class="form-check">
                                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="changePassword">
                                <label class="form-check-label" for="changePassword">
                                    Cambiar contraseña
                                </label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="passwordFields" class="d-none">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                    <label for="newPassword" class="form-label">Nueva contraseña</label>
                                    <div class="input-group">
                                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="newPassword" placeholder="Ingrese nueva contraseña">
                                        <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" type="button" onclick="togglePassword('newPassword')">
                                            <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                                        </button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                    <label for="confirmNewPassword" class="form-label">Confirmar nueva contraseña</label>
                                    <div class="input-group">
                                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="confirmNewPassword" placeholder="Confirme nueva contraseña">
                                        <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" type="button" onclick="togglePassword('confirmNewPassword')">
                                            <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                                        </button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cancelar</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Guardar cambios</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Modal Deshabilitar Empleado -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="disableEmployeeModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="disableEmployeeModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="disableEmployeeModalLabel">Deshabilitar Empleado</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>¿Está seguro de que desea deshabilitar al empleado <strong>Carlos Rodríguez</strong>?</p>
                    <p>El empleado no podrá acceder al sistema mientras esté deshabilitado.</p>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="disableReason" class="form-label">Motivo de la deshabilitación</label>
                        <textarea class="form-control" id="disableReason" rows="3" placeholder="Ingrese el motivo de la deshabilitación"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cancelar</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning">Deshabilitar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Modal Habilitar Empleado -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="enableEmployeeModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="enableEmployeeModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="enableEmployeeModalLabel">Habilitar Empleado</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>¿Está seguro de que desea habilitar al empleado <strong>Laura Martínez</strong>?</p>
                    <p>El empleado podrá volver a acceder al sistema.</p>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="enableReason" class="form-label">Notas de la habilitación</label>
                        <textarea class="form-control" id="enableReason" rows="3" placeholder="Ingrese notas opcionales"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cancelar</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-success">Habilitar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

   </body>
</html>
